OL,3,CWarning as man dies from 'catastrophic
OL,4,Cinjuries' after one punch
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of a taxi
OL,7,Fdriver has ruled that it was caused by
OL,8,F"catastrophic injuries" from a single
OL,9,Fpunch.
OL,11,FRoy Bester, 62, was cycling home along
OL,12,FAlbert Street when he became involved
OL,13,Fin a row with a 17-year-old car driver
OL,14,Fwho wanted to overtake him.
OL,16,FWords and then punches were exchanged
OL,17,Fwith Mr Bester falling to the ground.
