OL,6,FHe was taken to the General Hospital
OL,7,Fwhere he was found to have suffered a
OL,8,Fstroke, a bleed on the brain and
OL,9,Ffacial injuries.
OL,11,FMr Bester was flown to a specialist
OL,12,Funit at University Hospital
OL,13,FSouthampton where he had to be put
OL,14,Finto an induced coma.
OL,16,FHe was brought back to Jersey's
OL,17,Fhospital where he died, 17 days after
OL,18,Fthe incident.
