OL,6,FThe teenage boy, who cannot be named
OL,7,Ffor legal reasons, was but argued it
OL,8,Fwas self-defence and he was found not
OL,9,Fguilty by a jury after they saw CCTV
OL,10,Ffootage which showed Mr Bester had
OL,11,Fthrown the first punch.
OL,13,FSummarising at Mr Bester's inquest,
OL,14,FJersey Coroner Cyril Whelan said he
OL,15,Fhad died as a result of "catastrophic
OL,16,Finjuries" and it showed the dangers of
OL,17,Fa single punch.
